Subject line

Describe what you did and why. This is usually anywhere from a couple of
sentences and to a paragraph. If you have to write more than that, there is
probably too much in this one commit and you should probably divide it into
smaller commits.

#________________________________________________@______________________
#
#   * Limit the subject line to 50 characters
#   * Wrap the body at 72 characters
#   * Capitalize the subject line
#   * Do not end the subject line with a period
#   * Write the subject line to sound like an authoritative command
#   * Use the body to explain what and why vs. how
#
